Class VisualList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • peril.views.slick.util.Viewable
      • peril.views.slick.util.Clickable
        • peril.views.slick.components.VisualList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of this lists elements.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Component

    public final class VisualList<T>
extends Clickable
implements Component
    Encapsulates the behaviours a List of VisualList.Elements that can be displayed on screen and clicked on screen.

    2018-03-08
    Version:
    1.01.02
    Author:
    Joshua_Eddy
